Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Elevator Represents an elevator in an elevator simulation.
ElevatorBank The Queues that the waiting passengers are stored in has been updated to be a custom designed Queue called Elevator Queue.
ElevatorQueue This Queue is linked list that implements Queue.
ElevatorQueue.numPassangers This Compares two ElevatorQueue's based on their size.
ElevatorSimulation Simulates the operation of a bank of elevators.
Landscape Added a new data field that will hold the ElevatorBank ( as a SimObject ) and update with the advance() method
LandscapeDisplay Displays a Landscape graphically using Swing.
Passenger Represents a passenger in an elevator Simulation.
Passenger.MaxFloor Compares two passengers by target floor, where passenger P1 is considered greater than passenger P2 if P1.targetFloor > P2.targetFloor.
Passenger.MinFloor Compares two passengers by target floor, where passenger P1 is considered greater than passenger P2 if P1.targetFloor < P2.targetFloor.
PassengerGroup Represents a collection of passengers traveling in an elevator.
QueueSorter This class will act as a Priority queue for ElevatorQueues.
SimObject Represents an object in a simulation.
SimObjectList A List implementation that maintains a list of SimObjects.
 

Enum Summary
Elevator.Action Represents the current action as directed by the Elevator Bank.
Elevator.Direction Represents the current traveling state of an elevator.
ElevatorBank.STRATEGY This holds the different strategies that can be set for the simulation
